        Produces a two-dimensional scatter diagram.
        Parameters:
        frametitle - title of DatanGraphicsFrame; if frameTitle is blank the no DatanGraphicsFrame is initialized.
        filename - name of Postscript file - has to end with either ".ps" (for postscript) or ".eps" (for encapsulated postscript). If filename is blank, no file is initialized.
        x - x coordinates of points to be plotted
        y - y coordinates of points to be plotted
        xa - lower limit in x of computing coordinates
        xb - upper limit in x of computing coordinates
        ya - lower limit in y of computing coordinates
        yb - upper limit in y of computing coordinates
        textX - text for x axis
        textY - text for y axis
        caption - text for caption of plot
